  "projectDescription": "DAAAM (Describe Anything, Anywhere, at Any Moment) is a real-time foundation-model-first robot mapping system that combines SAM segmentation, BotSort tracking, and VLM grounding to build 4D Dynamic Scene Graphs on the fly.",
