  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time SAM/FastSAM/SAM2 segmentation with TensorRT acceleration",
    "BotSort temporal tracking with CLIP ReID for cross-frame object consistency",
    "Describe Anything Model (DAM) grounding for semantic object labeling",
    "Hierarchical 4D Dynamic Scene Graph construction via Hydra integration",
    "Optimization-based frame assignment (CVXPY MIP) for efficient grounding",
    "ROS 2 interface for live robot data streams",
    "Agentic scene understanding with LLM tool-calling over the scene graph",
    "State-of-the-art performance on NaVQA and SG3D benchmarks"
  ],
